awn Dollin and Andrew|last=Ferguson|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f9f025; width:3em;\"|\u2020\n|Denotes years in which Smith won a [[Rugby League World Cup|World Cup]] Title\n|-\n| style=\"background:#afe6ba; width:3em;\"|\u2020\n|Denotes years in which Smith won a [[Rugby League Four Nations|Four Nations]] Title\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"  style=\"font-size:90%; text-align:center; width:85%;\"\n|-\n!width=2%|Season\n!width=8%|Team\n!width=2%|Matches\n!width=2%|T\n!width=2%|G\n!width=2%|GK %\n!width=2%|F/G\n!width=2%|Pts\n!width=2%|W\n!width=2%|L\n!width=2%|D\n!width=2%|W-L %\n|-\n|- style=\"background-color: #EAEAEA\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal\"| 2006\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Australia national rugby league team|Australia]]\n| 5|| 0|| 0|| \u2014|| 0|| 0|| 4|| 1|| 0|| 80.00\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal\"| 2007\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Australia national rugby league team|Australia]]\n| 2|| 1|| 6|| 60.00|| 0|| 16|| 2|| 0|| 0|| 100.00\n|- style=\"background-color: #EAEAEA\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal\"| 2008\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Australia national rugby league team|Australia]]\n| 6|| 1|| 1|| 100.00|| 0|| 6|| 5|| 1|| 0|| 83.33\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#afe6ba; font-weight:normal\"| 2009\u2020\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Australia national rugby league team|Australia]]\n| 4|| 2|| 0|| \u2014|| 0|| 8|| 3|| 0|| 1|| 75.00\n|- style=\"background-color: #EAEAEA\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal\"| 2010\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Australia national rugby league team|Australia]]\n| 5|| 1|| 15|| 71.42|| 0|| 34|| 4|| 1|| 0|| 80.00\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#afe6ba; font-weight:normal\"| 2011\u2020\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Australia national rugby league team|Australia]]\n| 6|